To run using Evothings:
- open evothings workbench
- navigate to the folder Bullshyp-dataCollection/www
- drag index.html to evothings workbench
- run evothings on smartphone and connect to the computer
- run code from evothings workbench

To run using Cordova
- install cordova as shown here http://evothings.com/doc/build/cordova-install-windows.html
- connect smartphone to computer via USB
- run the following commands
  - cordova platforms add android
  - cordova run android

see this page for help: https://cordova.apache.org/docs/en/4.0.0/guide_platforms_android_index.md.html
